pageContext.claim: “Many of the court cases being filed all over the Country are not ours, but rather those of people that have seen horrible abuses. Our big cases showing the unconstitutionality of the 2020 Election, & the outrage of things that were done to change the outcome, will soon be filed!”
pageContext.analysis: Trump is offering an excuse for the failure of some many lawsuits filed by allies on his behalf. His own lawsuits did not fare any better.
